{"tid":1423091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會 資料整合小組","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:19:39.000Z","uid":12633,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"682bc31b6887e626185852629a803608e513645a","tid":1423091,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"幫朋友出post：<br />\n小妹見民間記者會其實做得好有noise好成功，都有好多人例如記者&amp;編輯俾左feedback，但係就冇乜人做過整合：<br />\n應該係話有好多人想幫手做但係眼見未有一個grp去gather人手，所以想開返個tg grp搵返有興趣幫手嘅巴絲詳談。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">始終今次運動嘅其中一個重點係無大台，所以呢個grp嘅工作只係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 整合各界人士針對記者會比嘅意見<br />\n2. 聽返政府/警方記招  記低佢地講嘅pt <br />\n留意佢地嘅手法（例如6號警察記招播片）<br />\n3. 集思廣益如何反攻敵方嘅論點<br />\n4. 集思廣益拆Q&amp;A有機會出現嘅問題</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目的只有一個，就係想方便返下一次想再開民間記者會嘅手足，務求可以令每一次記者會做得更精彩。<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">申報：<br />\n本tg group與 「民間記者會」組織 毫無關係，純粹希望集合港人智慧，為未來 民間有機會出現之 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">任何</span>記者會 提供參考資料，幫助文宣；採用與否，自行取決。</span>"},{"pid":"e8ce77d5ff82c0606cc89f4aef92e4adb1beb7c5","tid":1423091,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"代人post Group link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LUFmwxe9X3_iOAjmsB7Oxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLUFmwxe9X3_iOAjmsB7Oxw&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=5fa93d30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LUFmwxe9X3_iOAjmsB7Oxw</a>"},{"pid":"5cd77342a959165f2e7473fef3ca27a0249a0893","tid":1423091,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:53:38.000Z","msg":"專業關公 記者會 歡迎Q&amp;A<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b8a43bee6c0188ac62de9e67c0fde0124b9a5de0","tid":1423091,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:59:09.000Z"